 text-foreground mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"How Many Endings Does Pierrot Have?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The community has confirmed three endings on Pierrot's route: one standard ending, one secret ending, and one corrupted ending found in unused game files. The standard ending unlocks through normal play, while the secret ending requires specific refusal conditions. The corrupted ending remains unverified — no player has legitimately unlocked it.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Pierrot's endings are notable for their narrative complexity. Unlike other characters whose endings resolve their storylines, Pierrot's endings suggest that the circus itself is aware of the player and that repeated playthroughs are not separate attempts but continuations of a single narrative.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Smile For Me — Standard Ending\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"STANDARD\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Difficulty: Normal\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The standard ending for Pierrot's route triggers when players accept his offer during the garden scene in Act III. This is the ending most players see on their first playthrough and serves as the baseline for understanding Pierrot's character arc.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Unlock Conditions\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-2 text-on-surface-variant text-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"• Select \\\\\\\"Accept\\\\\\\" in the garden scene (Scene 9)\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"• Maintain positive dialogue choices throughout Acts I and II\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"• Do not refuse more than two dialogue interactions in the final act\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The ending concludes with Pierrot removing his mask, revealing a face that the player cannot clearly see. The screen fades to white as carnival music plays. Post-credits, a brief scene shows the garden empty with a single red thread on the ground.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Eternal Silence — Secret Ending\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-blood border border-blood/30 px-2 py-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"SECRET\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Difficulty: Hard\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Eternal Silence is Pierrot's secret ending and one of the most discussed outcomes in the community. It requires refusing every major dialogue interaction during the final act, turning silence into a deliberate narrative choice that breaks the game's contract with the player.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Unlock Conditions\\\"}],\\\"$Lf\\\"]}],\\\"$L10\\\",\\\"$L11\\\"]}],\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"$L13\\\",\\\"$L14\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"7:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface border-t border-outline/10 w-full\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-16 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"img\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/favicon-32x32.png\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Freak Circus Hub\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded-sm\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"FREAK CIRCUS HUB\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant opacity-60\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"© 2026\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs text-on-surface-variant opacity-60 text-center max-w-md\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Not affiliated with the original game or its developers. All trademarks belong to their respective owners.\\\",\\\" \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"a\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"mailto:hello@freak-circus.com\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"underline hover:text-primary transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Contact us for removal requests\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L15\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/privacy-policy\\\",\\\"className\\\":